# Tables
Basic syntax:
At the start of the line the end and the start of the table
#code(assets/code/tableExamples.txt)

**Examples:**


Vertical table (default)
#table v
Name|Score|State
Alice|95|Pass
Bob|87|Pass
#endtable

Horizontal table
#table h
Name|Score|State
Alice|95|Pass
Bob|87|Pass
#endtable

Both sides table, the space in the first line is optional, it does not affect, is for better visual understanding

#table b
     Name|Score
Yestarday|Leo|95
    Today|Bob|87
#endtable

Undefined mode table (Is a vertical table)
#table
Title|Description
Item 1|Text
Item 2|More text
#endtable